The United Nations proposed yesterday in Canc√∫n a plan for the renovation of domestic, commercial and industrial lighting in 100 countries to achieve a greenhouse gas reduction (GES) that corresponds almost to a third of the additional reduction needed to stabilize the global climate by 2020.
